Jack Rodwell made his first outing in a Sunderland shirt as late goals from Steven Fletcher and Connor Wickham saw the Black Cats win their latest pre-season friendly.

With the game goalless and seemingly staying that way, Fletcher broke the deadlock with a typical poacher's goal with 11 minutes remaining.

Latching on to a loose ball in the box, the Scotland international made no mistake from close range.

